[Java] Class ApplicationVariantImpl

        • com.android.build.gradle.internal.api.ApplicationVariantImpl
        • All Implemented Interfaces and Traits:
          ApplicationVariant, TestedVariant

          public class ApplicationVariantImpl
extends ApkVariantImpl

          implementation of the ApplicationVariant interface around an ApplicationVariantData object. This is a wrapper around the internal data model, in order to control what is accessible through the external API.
